    {
      "id": "narrative-story-membership-note",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Minimal Narrative Core",
      "position": {
        "x": 1080,
        "y": -90
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Minimal Narrative Core\n\nApprove in v1:\n- `character`\n- `location`\n- `event`\n- `scene`\n- `artifact`\n\nDefer:\n- `faction`\n- `motif`\n- `timeline-beat`\n- `relationship-note`\n\nThis keeps the first implementation anchored to concrete authored structure instead of literary analysis.",
        "_classBinding": {
