      "width": 500,
      "height": 420,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Narrative Pressures\n\nLikely typed relationships:\n- `character` appears in `scene`\n- `event` occurs at `location`\n- `scene` contains `event`\n- `character` holds or seeks `artifact`\n\nRuntime pressure:\n- reusable cast and location references\n- time ordering / sequence views\n- summary surfaces for arcs or episodes\n- maybe graph nesting if `scene` becomes structural\n\nStatus:\n- package root created\n- template created\n- class artifacts created\n- deferred narrative-analysis types remain out of v1",
